title: Seriously, What's Up With Brazil? with Paulo Figueiredo Filho and Rich Baris
itunes:title: Seriously, What's Up With Brazil? with Paulo Figueiredo Filho and Rich Baris
description:
Despite his party doing well and despite holding a lead early on election night, Brazil's conservative president Jair Bolsonaro just suffered a narrow defeat. Sound familiar? Journalist Paulo Figueiredo Filho joins to explain Brazil's elections, the possibility of fraud, and whether the country is at real risk the military intervening in the vote. Then, Rich Baris breaks down the Democrats' disintegrating position with Hispanic voters.
